title: Sky High - Radio Drama
description:
1 x 45 mins

It is the day of Cissie & Fred's Diamond Wedding anniversary. A cloud is cast over what should be a happy day by the thought that in a few days, their council tower block is to be demolished, and the old couple moved in to an Old People's Home, something Cissie resents. After their visitors have left, tragedy strikes and Cissie decides upon her own course of action. A poignant tale about love and loss
